                "item_values": [],
                "key": "Rule by Thunder",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>Increases ATK by <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">20%/25%/30%/35%/40%</span> and grants the might of the Thunder Emblem. At stack levels 1/2/3, the Thunder Emblem increases Normal Attack DMG by <span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">12%/24%/40%</span> | <span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">15%/30%/50%</span> | <span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">18%/36%/60%</span> | <span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">21%/42%/70%</span> | <span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">24%48%/80%</span>. The character will obtain 1 stack of Thunder Emblem in each of the following scenarios: Normal Attack deals DMG (stack lasts 5s), casting Elemental Skill (stack lasts 10s); Energy is less than 100% (stack disappears when Energy is full). Each stack's duration is calculated independently.</p>"
                ]
              },
